Name: ConceptualComponentModuleName
Description: A name for the ConceptualComponentModule. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the ConceptualComponentModule. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the ConceptualComponentModule. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: Coverage
Description: Provides information about the topical, spatial, and temporal coverage of the conceptual components included in this module.

Name: ConceptSchemeReference
Description: Contains a set of the concepts measured by the data that are being documented.

Name: UniverseSchemeReference
Description: Contains a set of the Universes and sub-universes of the data that are being documented.

Name: GeographicStructureSchemeReference
Description: Contains a collection of geographic structures.

Name: GeographicLocationSchemeReference
Description: Contains a collection of geographic locations.

Name: UnitTypeSchemeReference
Description: Contains a collection of unit types.
